                <supplied reason="lost" cert="low">--- lib(ertus)</supplied> <expan><abbr>Ser</abbr><ex>gia</ex></expan> Perseus ob honorem VIviratus fori et basilicae in<lb break="no" n="2"/><supplied reason="lost">tercolumnia<certainty locus="name" match="preceding-sibling::text()" cert="low"/> cum ca</supplied>ncellis et trabaec<expan><ex>u</ex><abbr>lis</abbr></expan> <note>sic</note> et postibus pecunia sua exornata &amp;lt;d&amp;gt;edit
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
